 <name>padthv1</name>
 <summary>an old-school polyphonic additive synthesizer</summary>
 <description>
  <p>padthv1 is an old-school polyphonic additive synthesizer
  with stereo fx.</p>
  <p>features:<ul>
  <li>pure stand-alone JACK client with JACK-session, NSM and both JACK MIDI
    and ALSA MIDI input support;</li>
  <li>LV2 instrument plugin.
    URI: http://padthv1.sourceforge.net/lv2</li>
  </ul></p>
 </description>
